creator: DigiSEq
descriptionHtml:
Why download many wearable management apps when you can download just one?

Manage-Mii is the mobile app platform that allows you to control contactless functionality across different wearable device brands supported by DIGISEQ.

With Manage-Mii, you can manage one user account among multiple branded wearables, in one app. Our mobile platform allows you link your wearable to your personal credentials, add a contactless service to your device e.g. payment, track your service’s activity, change your details paired with your wearable, or even freeze your service operation in case you lose your wearable.

Manage-Mii is only compatible with a selective group of wearable brands. These supported brands are listed on our website: https://www.manage-mii.co.uk/
